About Scholastic Schools Catalog

Learn more about our platform and mission

Our Mission

To provide comprehensive, accurate, and accessible information about educational institutions across Zimbabwe, empowering parents, students, and educators to make informed decisions about education.

We believe that every child deserves access to quality education, and every parent should have the information they need to choose the right school for their child.

Advanced Search

Find schools based on multiple criteria including location, curriculum, facilities, and academic performance.

Detailed Profiles

Comprehensive school profiles with photos, facilities, academic programs, fee structures, and reviews.

Ratings & Reviews

Authentic reviews from parents, students, and alumni to help you make informed decisions.

Location Services

Interactive maps and location-based search to find schools near you.

Data Sources & Accuracy

Our database is compiled from multiple verified sources:

  • Official school registrations and accreditation data
  • Ministry of Education publications and reports
  • School websites and official communications
  • Verified user submissions and updates
  • Annual school performance reports

We regularly update our database to ensure accuracy and timeliness of information.
